  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "CEYPETCO \u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b9f\u0bc0\u0b9a\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Diesel for CEYPETCO is coming",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Energy Minister Kanchana Wijesekara said that the ship loaded with 40,000 metric tons of diesel purchased by CEYPETCO will arrive in Sri Lanka on July 8 or 9."
      ],
